sequenceDiagram
  participant Client as MCP client / Agent
  participant Shrink as caveman-shrink proxy
  participant Server as Upstream MCP server

  Client->>Shrink: initialize / list request
  Shrink->>Server: forward request unchanged
  Server-->>Shrink: tools/list, prompts/list, resources/list response
  Shrink->>Shrink: compress configured prose fields
  Shrink-->>Client: return shorter metadata

  Client->>Shrink: tools/call request
  Shrink->>Server: forward tool call unchanged
  Server-->>Shrink: tool result
  Shrink-->>Client: pass result unchanged

  Note over Shrink: Basis: caveman-shrink README. Source-level JSON-RPC behavior pending verification.
